{"tid":504212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報：朱經緯2016年揮動警棍制止旺角暴亂","createTime":"2017-12-19T16:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:44:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":50,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3a17ddd24aba7b6f1c10a73074dc7c59fc2c41","tid":504212,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/25446109_1740245749348484_4183198812545678455_n.jpg?oh=c060cb5576bfd77544ddb87a1c5a6d1f&amp;oe=5AC4E231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F25446109_1740245749348484_4183198812545678455_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dc060cb5576bfd77544ddb87a1c5a6d1f%26oe%3D5AC4E231&h=11e90c23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93e40dff2103c24a7c1c798676ec8b77bf074c57","tid":504212,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/finance/text/2017/1219/133967.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Ffinance%2Ftext%2F2017%2F1219%2F133967.html&d=80XwKyNif%2BPBT4zMP7aBV%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f2772d96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/finance/text/2017/1219/133967.html</a><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯，被控二○一六年在旺角街頭用警棍毆打市民鄭仲恆，經冗長審訊後，昨日在東區裁判法院被控「襲擊」罪名成立，即時收押，下周判刑。<br />\n<br />\n　　不少市民在電視新聞中看到已逾中年的朱經緯步入法院，隨後被押上囚車離去的鏡頭，心中不免都會有一絲惆悵以至難以釋懷之感：身為執法人員的朱經緯，為何會落得個如此不堪的下場？<br />\n<br />\n　　當然，作為市民大眾，理應尊重法院裁決，不應有過多的質疑，但是，朱經緯案由發生到裁決，實在有太多令人「諗唔通」的地方。<br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">市民大眾都還清楚記得，案發之日，即二○一六年大年初一深夜的旺角街頭，那是一個什麼樣的駭人場面？當晚數以千計的民眾在激進反對派的挑唆下到旺角街頭聚集，行人路上的紅磚被撬起當成武器擲向到來維持秩序的警員，垃圾桶橫飛，棍棒竹枝和自製盾牌大批運到，警方這邊驅散，人群轉眼又到街道的另一邊聚集&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\n<br />\n　　顯然，從在電視上重複播出的資料片段中可見，當晚朱經緯確實有揮動過手中警棍，警棍也「的而且確」落到了一名男子的背部，但這些都是一片混亂和「電光火石」間的事。<br />\n<br />\n　　同樣，毫無疑問，沒有人會認同警方打人是可以接受的行為；但是，<span style=\"color: red;\">當晚旺角街頭亟需實施人群管制，以制止暴亂和暴力襲警</span>，一些必要的、目的在恢復治安秩序的武力又是否完全可以避免？<br />\n<br />\n　　因此，當晚朱經緯的行為，可以說是在執行職務過程中不當或過度使用武力，但眼前朱經緯被控的罪名是「襲擊」。「襲擊」與「不當使用武力」是兩回事，前者性質與刑罰都較後者嚴重。但「襲擊」應是有企圖或有目的，而當時的朱經緯，又有什麼「襲擊」鄭仲恆的意圖或目的呢？"},{"pid":"94ad768c2df2ed05fa5e36dffb300bd9fc5ca132","tid":504212,"uid":20058,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"我屌你笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068765eed84e0ef4c39163227b261725eb5ef634","tid":504212,"uid":12947,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:28:20.000Z","msg":"咩意圖？發洩囉on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8ce1c62b4eaaf34bf8525bec7393984434488b","tid":504212,"uid":134323,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，不如話結束左二戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eeabaa9c25ff91b53390188a34c68fc9acc8ed","tid":504212,"uid":7369,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"原來仲有一單，告多次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa754185f86e52b7459813ee0271697b4cbc7902","tid":504212,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b95c30d8aa38605f949341c29f907e38f2cd1d","tid":504212,"uid":9732,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"令到自己爽算唔算意圖，當班市民螞蟻咁打，有一種君臨天下既感覺"},{"pid":"cd94f8d796a2593488aba4f2a4821f3a6f59bc9a","tid":504212,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b37b6bdf321520ac90f93fac81ca383f47f76207","tid":504212,"uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141127/large/27la2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141127%2Flarge%2F27la2p1.jpg&h=4b5a3421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6ef0ed99cdda966a583c9f2b687d4c431ab17ee","tid":504212,"uid":103207,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"【奇文共賞】左報「爆」朱經緯涉另一襲擊案 魚蛋革命再揮棍？ <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&d=80XwKyNif%2BPBT4zMP7aBV%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c34b4cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&h=b44751f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518</a>"},{"pid":"9fa5730b4bad9ea3efe6ccf3cc1a569b4df7eaa0","tid":504212,"uid":103207,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【奇文共賞】左報「爆」朱經緯涉另一襲擊案 魚蛋革命再揮棍？ <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&d=80XwKyNif%2BPBT4zMP7aBV%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c34b4cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&h=b44751f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518</a></blockquote><br />\n 前警司朱經緯揮警棍襲擊途人，昨日被判罪成還柙等候本月29日判刑。今日《大公報》「小社論」《井水集》就替朱sir抱不平，力撐當晚朱的行為「可以說是在執行職務過程中不當或過度使用武力」，不算「襲擊」，因為「當晚旺角街頭亟需實施人群管制，以制止暴亂和暴力襲警」云云。<br />\n<br />\n文中當晚，所指何時？文章開首已稱朱「被控二○一六年在旺角街頭用警棍毆打市民鄭仲恆」，中段更對「當晚」發生的事件過程仔細描述，「<span style=\"color: red;\">案發之日，即二○一六年大年初一深夜的旺角街頭，那是一個甚麼樣的駭人場面</span>」、「行人路上的紅磚被撬起當成武器擲向到來維持秩序的警員，垃圾桶橫飛，棍棒竹枝和自製盾牌大批運到」，歷歷在目、鉅細無遺，恍若親歷其境。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，朱經緯被指控的襲擊案件發生於2014年12月，亦即佔領運動時期、旺角佔領區被清場後，市民「響應」時任特首梁振英呼籲，到旺角「鳩嗚、購物」致大批人群聚集而發生，<span style=\"color: red;\">朱經緯亦已於2015年7月正式退休</span>。《大公》文章撰文者，似乎將「鳩嗚」與「魚蛋革命」兩事，完全混淆了。"},{"pid":"6460f1b0e69c9c59c9e3b990e54a653101377497","tid":504212,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3adf3ab702d806d2dca63b35499934a088901c","tid":504212,"uid":75765,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"制止了第三次世界大戰"},{"pid":"5c16403fb0c7b14460e21ea0f57109f6aa3ebdec","tid":504212,"uid":103207,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"2015年揮的棍制止了2016的暴動"},{"pid":"eb78d3882534b1b5aa2c06e7635451ad6984202e","tid":504212,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"棋差一著&hellip;&hellip;沒有一間店鋪被爆破"},{"pid":"50e7985ee2ad46d8728fbe7d37aea10d3f7132b5","tid":504212,"uid":129664,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>【奇文共賞】左報「爆」朱經緯涉另一襲擊案 魚蛋革命再揮棍？ <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&d=80XwKyNif%2BPBT4zMP7aBV%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c34b4cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&h=b44751f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518</a></blockquote><br />\n 前警司朱經緯揮警棍襲擊途人，昨日被判罪成還柙等候本月29日判刑。今日《大公報》「小社論」《井水集》就替朱sir抱不平，力撐當晚朱的行為「可以說是在執行職務過程中不當或過度使用武力」，不算「襲擊」，因為「當晚旺角街頭亟需實施人群管制，以制止暴亂和暴力襲警」云云。<br />\n<br />\n文中當晚，所指何時？文章開首已稱朱「被控二○一六年在旺角街頭用警棍毆打市民鄭仲恆」，中段更對「當晚」發生的事件過程仔細描述，「<span style=\"color: red;\">案發之日，即二○一六年大年初一深夜的旺角街頭，那是一個甚麼樣的駭人場面</span>」、「行人路上的紅磚被撬起當成武器擲向到來維持秩序的警員，垃圾桶橫飛，棍棒竹枝和自製盾牌大批運到」，歷歷在目、鉅細無遺，恍若親歷其境。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，朱經緯被指控的襲擊案件發生於2014年12月，亦即佔領運動時期、旺角佔領區被清場後，市民「響應」時任特首梁振英呼籲，到旺角「鳩嗚、購物」致大批人群聚集而發生，<span style=\"color: red;\">朱經緯亦已於2015年7月正式退休</span>。《大公》文章撰文者，似乎將「鳩嗚」與「魚蛋革命」兩事，完全混淆了。</blockquote><br />\n2015年退休，案發係2016年，即係當時佢唔係警察，唔係執行職務，即係一個黐線佬係街度亂咁打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49a2152b8de2aa85c86f66af855d0ee78ba315e","tid":504212,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線，不如話結束左二戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3ff6b7ce3ea3972b4de027b9473f6090ca8055","tid":504212,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"曼加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6142fba230a0fc79349fa7d1558710ff0d354dd0","tid":504212,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"平行時空"},{"pid":"84100d02d83e285c50d81a3851dd86f8f1dfcd34","tid":504212,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"連日期都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bf06159cf6e98ea4a9ae167b2c86faf0b2521b","tid":504212,"uid":59695,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/021333_4977e36f94a60a223c290b5edd17c7f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F021333_4977e36f94a60a223c290b5edd17c7f2.jpg&h=9e470c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66488a53d0699c0604d86b473596318ae0d07cb0","tid":504212,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:25:38.000Z","msg":"原來係朱sir一棍毆出魚彈革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c74d09f3204b3296a78ce43185a8192f096b63","tid":504212,"uid":36995,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"大公報妓者係咪流晒口水既弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a730d281996f35edf90b35633f20ada5144f90c","tid":504212,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:32:55.000Z","msg":"柒到"},{"pid":"33f47269799296740fbbe2313b1fa43f479911ad","tid":504212,"uid":61589,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T23:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2015年揮的棍制止了2016的暴動</blockquote><br />\n用明朝既尚方寶劍斬清朝既官"},{"pid":"7fe2dfa2e46cee975e855792c2885a92ab272a6b","tid":504212,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"平行時空"},{"pid":"20b5a7744ef9672cd977b2ee3b2f5e4a84af74a7","tid":504212,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"大公妓者=社會垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fd32e73388e52ea437e52a52b900069d020935","tid":504212,"uid":128014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大公報妓者係咪流晒口水既弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望到你個username差少少中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3961fcf8953f5d4ad479a8832fc0d0e13b409e18","tid":504212,"