ike":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"d黨報真係寧舍on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc94b3248c0f61dc6b3cc52dab6cb767eb71f36","tid":504212,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc158b90836feced3d6c00c0a93c9cd9fea46b34","tid":504212,"uid":56657,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:17:28.000Z","msg":"豬sir個日唔係差佬，又手持武器係現場打人，算唔算暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"aa26ebe2bf2bf5119fe3be2afbecf4a5d7e0337b","tid":504212,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬sir個日唔係差佬，又手持武器係現場打人，算唔算暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n一定係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b417372b230bf4f3c033536ec6af883df1f2fc","tid":504212,"uid":14244,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfea28b73f182cb5a9cb5d747540ac454a17d144","tid":504212,"uid":28277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:21:49.000Z","msg":"佢砌朱sir 生豬肉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108da64dcbb3c40c1ebc017fb14af5b635c6bc5","tid":504212,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:22:41.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e5b91b3d5528f2dc99a88f9669ec368eb26507","tid":504212,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T01:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>【奇文共賞】左報「爆」朱經緯涉另一襲擊案 魚蛋革命再揮棍？ <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&d=80XwKyNif%2BPBT4zMP7aBV%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c34b4cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57602518&h=b44751f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57602518</a></blockquote><br />\n 前警司朱經緯揮警棍襲擊途人，昨日被判罪成還柙等候本月29日判刑。今日《大公報》「小社論」《井水集》就替朱sir抱不平，力撐當晚朱的行為「可以說是在執行職務過程中不當或過度使用武力」，不算「襲擊」，因為「當晚旺角街頭亟需實施人群管制，以制止暴亂和暴力襲警」云云。<br />\n<br />\n文中當晚，所指何時？文章開首已稱朱「被控二○一六年在旺角街頭用警棍毆打市民鄭仲恆」，中段更對「當晚」發生的事件過程仔細描述，「<span style=\"color: red;\">案發之日，即二○一六年大年初一深夜的旺角街頭，那是一個甚麼樣的駭人場面</span>」、「行人路上的紅磚被撬起當成武器擲向到來維持秩序的警員，垃圾桶橫飛，棍棒竹枝和自製盾牌大批運到」，歷歷在目、鉅細無遺，恍若親歷其境。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，朱經緯被指控的襲擊案件發生於2014年12月，亦即佔領運動時期、旺角佔領區被清場後，市民「響應」時任特首梁振英呼籲，到旺角「鳩嗚、購物」致大批人群聚集而發生，<span style=\"color: red;\">朱經緯亦已於2015年7月正式退休</span>。《大公》文章撰文者，似乎將「鳩嗚」與「魚蛋革命」兩事，完全混淆了。</blockquote><br />\n2015年退休，案發係2016年，即係當時佢唔係警察，唔係執行職務，即係一個黐線佬係街度亂咁打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能仲冒警，要坐幾多碌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}